~Category~: System

~Syntax~: /reboot
~Syntax~: /reboot restart <seconds>
~Description~:
   Shuts down the server after <seconds> and automatically reboots.
   Code, maps and arches will be automatically updated.
   <seconds> has a minimum value of 30 for less than SAs.

~Syntax~: /reboot cancel
~Description~:
   Cancels any existing reboot requests.

~Syntax~: /reboot shutdown <seconds>
~Description~:
   Shuts down the server after <seconds>.
   ~No automatic restart!~
   <seconds> defaults to 0.
   Restricted to SAs only.
